        // Initialize the XL9555 device by configuring its registers
        // Configure port 0 direction (0x06) - all outputs by default
        // Configure port 1 direction (0x07) - all outputs by default
        // For typical usage, set all pins as outputs (0x00) and set initial state (0xFF for high)

